# picoGym Level 423: Secret of the Polyglot
Source: https://play.picoctf.org/practice/challenge/423

## Goal
The Network Operations Center (NOC) of your local institution picked up a suspicious file, they're getting conflicting information on what type of file it is.<br>
They've brought you in as an external expert to examine the file.<br>
Can you extract all the information from this strange file?<br>
Download the suspicious file here.<br>
https://artifacts.picoctf.net/c_titan/7/flag2of2-final.pdf

## What I learned
```
file can be opened many formats
```
